originalText.text: Last time I bought a facial cleanser and sunscreen here with my friends. Special praise to one woman, she is the best Chanel salesperson I have ever seen. She worked very hard to help me get the benefits and introduced me to how to use it in detail. Also helped me solve a lot of problems.

originalText.text: I had the best experience with Jasmine today at the Chanel makeup counter. The interaction was very graceful and understanding of my exhaustion in the moment. She easily identified the correct color match for my skin. Her experience and knowledge made the entire experience very comfortable. I will be back, thank you, Jasmine!

originalText.text: The guy who attends customers at Chanel store said some mean comments while we were checking out for cologne for my friend. The display pieces were empty and despite he saw us trying to try sampling several times in vain, he looked at us rendering no help and with some sort of suspicion and told there are thieves who run away with display bottles kept there. While such incidents maybe true but the way he looked at us and whole experience was very humiliating. It’s the responsibility of store keepers to make the customer experience as seamless as possible even if they have challenges handling shoplifters. I don’t think I will ever go back here.
